		CHANGES IN fun VERSION 0.1-0

NEW FEATURES

  o R can perform t-test, F test and so on, but sometimes we use R to
  test Alzheimer's disease; see alzheimer_test()

  o lights_out() to play the "Lights Out" game

  o mine_sweeper() to play the Minesweeper game

  o sliding_puzzle() to play the Sliding Puzzle

  o tower_of_hanoi() to watch the game Tower of Hanoi

  o gomoku(), the game of ``Five in a row''

  o and other interesting functions
